I '''Dame Agatha Mary Clarissa Christie''', [[Dame Commander of the Order of the British Empire|DBE]] (mibait yang '''Miller'''; 15 Setiembre 1890&nbsp;– 12 Enero 1976) metung yang Ingles a talasulat krimen (''crime writer'') a sinulat nobela, makuyad a salita ampong drama. Sinulat ya mu namang anam a ''[[romance novel|romances]]'' king lalam ning lagyung '''Mary Westmacott''', oneng pikabaluan yang dili kareng kayang 66 a nobelang detektib ampong 14 a koleksyon da reng makuyad a salita king sarili nang lagyu, at keraklan kareti makapatungkul la kareng imbestigasyun da reng tauan antimo i [[Hercule Poirot]], [[Miss Jane Marple]] ampong [[Tommy and Tuppence]]. Sinulat ne murin ing pekamalambat dang palageng drama king yatu, ing ''[[The Mousetrap]]''.<ref>{{cite web|title=The Mousetrap website|url=https://www.the-mousetrap.co.uk/online/default.asp|accessdate=24 December 2012}}</ref>

